EulerAngles Orientation::GetAsEuler (  ) 

Converts to a rotation matrix.

If the euler angle convention is being used then this function will set its arguments to the stored values otherwise the result is undefined. If the angle axis convention being used then this function will set its arugments to those values otherwise the result is undefined. If the quaternion convention being used then this function will set its arguments to those values otherwise the result is undefined. If the eigensystem convention is being used then this function will set its arguments to the appropriate values otherwise the result is undefined.
